flowchart TD
    A[Application requests memory] --> B{Allocation within<br/>cgroup limit?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Kernel grants memory]
    C --> D[Application continues]

    B -->|No| E[Kernel returns ENOMEM]
    E --> F{Allocator can<br/>free cached memory?}

    F -->|Yes| G[Retry allocation]
    G --> B

    F -->|No| H[Allocation failure]
    H --> I{Rust allocation<br/>error handler}

    I -->|Default handler| J[Process aborts]
    I -->|Custom handler| K[Application handles error]

    L[Memory pressure severe] --> M[OOM Killer invoked]
    M --> N[Process terminated<br/>with SIGKILL]
    N --> O[No cleanup runs]

    style J fill:#ff6b6b,stroke:#c92a2a,color:#fff
    style N fill:#ff6b6b,stroke:#c92a2a,color:#fff
    style O fill:#ff8787,stroke:#c92a2a,color:#fff
